Step 1: Start
Step 2: Move Input Value to Register
Step 3: Set Count as 4
Step 4: Move Register Value to Accumulator
Step 5: Send Accumulator Value to Output Port C0
Step 6: Move 1010 to BX
Step 7: Repeat Step 8 Till BX = 0
Step 8: Decrement BX
Step 9: Increment Input Register
Step 10: Decrement Count
Step 11: Go to Step 4 If Count != 0
Step 12: Go to Step 2
Step 13: Stop